{"tid":626261,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你有一舊錢 你會點揀？","createTime":"2018-04-12T03:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T05:58:01.000Z","uid":103133,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f763a521aa7459a6cc73240881db27fee4da70e1","tid":626261,"uid":103133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"假設你三十歲人 有百六萬係手<br />\n女朋友三十歲 同你一齊儲個百六萬<br />\n<br />\n你唸住用百六萬做首期<br />\n另外問屋企人借幾十萬黎做裝修<br />\n所以買左層四百萬既樓先<br />\n<br />\n但你女朋友就催婚 話結左婚先<br />\n但結完婚有一兩年係無樓比你地一齊住<br />\n你會結左婚先定買左樓先？<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：買樓然後結婚<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：結左婚先再儲返一兩年買樓"},{"pid":"a065d78144d830d28a12195dc7dbad4fc81cec5d","tid":626261,"uid":76063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:28:22.000Z","msg":"買樓 結婚細搞"},{"pid":"3c64bdbe15ac1554dfefd21babea63bc746929e7","tid":626261,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"你有百六萬想買四百萬<br />\n但係要問屋企人借錢裝修 <br />\n仲煩唔夠錢結婚<br />\n<br />\n其實我百四萬就買咗五百六萬樓<br />\n麻煩巴打你詳細 d 計條數嚟睇下"},{"pid":"7a29bb8f71114790e3f4807292b8f77733408262","tid":626261,"uid":125581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:37:57.000Z","msg":"而家仲有四球既樓揀？"},{"pid":"255bca7695aca6e28db3dd4ccf9970c294b40fb4","tid":626261,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"160萬夠買四百幾萬連裝修連結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n600萬按足都係120萬首期咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69cfd7664938dc6bef4758212a4162ba88c26cc","tid":626261,"uid":32583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"400萬樓首期40萬，你條數係點計"},{"pid":"432ffd4787cec052ab3dff73b35e435ce9e26f83","tid":626261,"uid":23385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"255bc